# The @buf scope is served from the Buf Schema Registry's generated-SDK npm registry,
# not npmjs.com. The pugsh/pug module is public, so NO auth token is needed. Do not
# add an `_authToken` here: a real token is a leaked account credential, and an empty one
# makes npm send a bad bearer token that the registry rejects with 401. (Matches sdk-node.)
@buf:registry=https://buf.build/gen/npm/v1/
